title: JUI Candidate Khalil-ur-Rehman wins PB-07 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Jamiat Ulema-e-Islam Pakistan (JUI) candidate Khalil-ur-Rehman has won the Balochistan Assembly election from PB-07, Ziarat cum Harnai by securing 25,256 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz (PML-N) Candidate who bagged 24,187 votes.
Overall voters turnout remained 57.41 percent.
